ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 132 - (Manitoba) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 132 - which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA with respect to the FOREST FIRES that affected an area northeast of Cranberry-Portage from June 15 to August 4, 2010.
